videos.headline: Miami (OH) takes back opening kickoff 97 yards for TD
videos.description: Maurice Thomas takes the opening kickoff 97 yards for a touchdown as Miami (OH) leads Western Michigan early.

videos.headline: Western Michigan QB completes 33-yard TD
videos.description: Jon Wassink finds Jayden Reed  for a 33-yard touchdown and his second of the day.

videos.headline: Wassink rushes in for game-winning Western Michigan TD
videos.description: Jon Wassink sneaks in the end zone for a game-winning touchdown as Miami (OH) falls to Western Michigan 40-39.
